			 appointed by the Majority Leader of the Senate, in consultation with the
			 Chairperson of the Committee on Indian Affairs of the Senate;

the obstacles to
			 nongovernmental financial support, such as from private foundations and
			 corporate charities, for programs benefitting Native children;

clause.text:
the adoption of
			 standard definitions and compatible systems platforms to allow for greater
			 linkage of data sets across Federal agencies;

the collection
			 and measurement of data that are useful to Indian tribes and Native
			 Hawaiians;

